{"tid":629650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTV影低 女文員險被色狼強姦 糾纏間途人開門營救","createTime":"2018-04-15T00:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T01:55:45.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"232f8151c283a395e59b2557ca2502e6a072c4db","tid":629650,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"在光天化日下竟持刀闖入一間店舖企圖強姦獨自看店的女文員，幸一名途人在店外看到女文員與其糾纏，當機立斷即介入制服色狼勇救她。<br />\n<br />\n案發在邊疆地區克拉斯諾亞爾斯克（Krasnoyarsk），當時正值午飯時間，一名身材矮小的色狼闖入店內視察，似乎看看店內有沒有其他人，當女文員葉卡捷琳娜（Ekaterina）干預時他即露出狼相，拿出小刀襲擊女事主。<br />\n<br />\n葉卡捷琳娜非常勇敢，企圖奪刀反抗並走向門口方向，糾纏間她倒地，正當色狼拉下她的裙子企圖為所欲為之際，途人維索斯基（Alexander Vysotsky）見不對勁，衝入內制服色狼，勇救葉卡捷琳娜。<br />\n<br />\n店內閉路電視拍下整個案發過程，當地傳媒均讚頌維索斯基是英雄，但他回應時謙稱：「在我那個處境下，任何人都會這樣做。我不認為自己是英雄，葉卡捷琳娜也做得很好，她做對了，將那色狼拉近門口，還緊握刀鋒。要是他將她帶到後面房間，恐怕她不能僅雙手受傷。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180414/large/1523688616_fbc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180414%2Flarge%2F1523688616_fbc3.jpg&h=ef91f614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180415/58070684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F58070684&d=3JZvmOjVobjbrusMEVzyyW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ee1bdf63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F58070684&h=6d686a83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180415/58070684</a><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n如果是香港發生，應該拍片或call 999多，直接單拖幫手好少"},{"pid":"8725dbe441655554718459d96d9002f27f6e2812","tid":629650,"uid":55386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"條女好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=